---
title: White Choc-Chip Cookie Bar with Peanut Butter Caramel Drizzle | Serves 4+
description: Trust us when we say, this cookie bar is the bee’s knees of scrumptious desserts. Like your favourite blonde brownie and cookie merged together, these fudgey delights are studded with dark chocolate chunks and finished off with a decadent gooey peanut caramel drizzled all over. Proceed with caution – these bad boys are addictive!

*Nutritional information is based on 8-10 servings*
